Package: sonic-openconfig-diagnostic-gateway
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9)
Maintainer: SONiC OpenConfig Team
Description: SONiC OpenConfig Diagnostic Gateway
 A network diagnostic gateway that exposes a REST API and uses
 gNMI/gNOI to probe and diagnose Cisco IOS XE interfaces via
 OpenConfig and Cisco-native YANG models.
 .
 Supports fixture mode for offline development and testing,
 live gNMI mode for real device interaction, safe interface
 description changes with audit logging, and gNOI capability
 probing with destructive operations intentionally disabled.
